Title: Not in Scotland Anymore
Writer: Diana Gabaldon (based on the series of books written by), Ronald D. Moore (developed by), Ira Steven Behr (written for television by)
Actors: Caitriona Balfe, Sam Heughan, Tobias Menzies, Duncan Lacroix
Plot: Claire and Jamie plan to infiltrate Royal Court of France to disrupt Jacobite Rebellion. Jamie is forced to deal with Prince Charlie in Paris Brothels.
